{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SVG","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  <strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/SVG/教學\">由此開始</a></strong>\n  本教程將輔助你開始使用 SVG。\n</p>\n<p>\n  <strong>可縮放向量圖形</strong> (Scalable Vector Graphics，SVG) 是用於描述二維向量圖形的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/XML\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">XML</a> 標記語言。基本上，SVG 用於圖形，而\n  XHTML 用於文字。\n</p>\n<p>\n  SVG 類似 Adobe 專有的 Flash 技術，SVG 與 Flash 兩者最大的分別在於 SVG 為 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C 所推薦</a> (即標準)，並以\n  XML 為基礎，而非封閉的二進制格式。SVG 設計為與其他 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C</a> 標準 (如 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a>、<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">DOM</a> 及 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/AudioVideo/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SMIL</a>) 一同運作。\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"為何使用_svg？","title":"為何使用 SVG？","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更好的圖形格式","title":"更好的圖形格式","isH3":true,"content":"<p>SVG 是一種向量圖形格式。向量圖形可縮可放，圖形完全不會失真，為像素圖形所不能及。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.croczilla.com/svg/samples/lion/lion.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Lion</a>, <a href=\"http://www.croczilla.com/svg/samples/butterfly/butterfly.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Butterfy</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://www.croczilla.com/svg/samples/tiger/tiger.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Tiger</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://plurib.us/1shot/2007/svg_gallery/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 藝術圖庫</a></li>\n  <li>更多範例 (<a href=\"http://www.croczilla.com/svg/samples/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 範例 croczilla.com</a>, <a href=\"http://www.carto.net/papers/svg/samples/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">carto.net</a>)</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"增強_html_內容的表現","title":"增強 HTML 內容的表現","isH3":true,"content":"<p>SVG 可和 HTML、CSS 及 JavaScript 一同運作。使用 SVG 增強普通 HTML 頁面或 web 應用程式。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>如何<a href=\"/zh-TW/SVG_In_HTML_Introduction\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">在 XHTML 中使用 SVG</a> 教程</li>\n  <li>Google <a href=\"https://maps.google.com\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Maps</a> (路徑圖) &amp; <a href=\"https://docs.google.com\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Docs</a> (試算表繪圖)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://starkravingfinkle.org/projects/demo/svg-bubblemenu-in-html.xml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 泡沫選單</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mozilla_裡的_svg","title":"Mozilla 裡的 SVG","isH3":false,"content":"<p>SVG 如何在 Mozilla 裡實作的註解和資訊。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Firefox 目前已實作 <a href=\"/en-US/SVG_in_Firefox\">SVG 1.1 規範</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://jwatt.org/svg/authoring/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 編寫指南</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/Mozilla_SVG_Project\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Mozilla SVG 專案</a>概述</li>\n  <li>有關 SVG 和 Mozilla 的<a href=\"/en-US/SVG/FAQ\">問答集</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"工具","title":"工具","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/Test/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG Test Suite</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://jiggles.w3.org/svgvalidator/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG Validator</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/Special:Tags?tag=SVG:Tools&amp;language=en\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">更多工具...</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"動畫和互動","title":"動畫和互動","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如同 HTML，SVG 也有一個 DOM、事件，並且可由 JavaScript 存取。這可讓開發者建立豐富的動畫和互動式圖形。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Firefox extension (<a href=\"http://schepers.cc/grafox/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Grafox</a>) to add a subset of SMIL animation support</li>\n  <li>Interactive <a href=\"http://people.mozilla.com/~vladimir/demos/photos.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">photos</a> manipulation</li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"http://starkravingfinkle.org/blog/2007/07/firefox-3-svg-foreignobject/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML transformations</a> using\n    SVG's <code>foreignObject</code>\n  </li>\n  <li>Animated <a href=\"http://lab.vodafone.com/vienna/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">art</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"繪圖、圖表、遊戲_3d_實驗","title":"繪圖、圖表、遊戲 &amp; 3D 實驗","isH3":false,"content":"<p>只需少許 SVG 即可增強網頁內容，這裡有一些重量級 SVG 用法的範例。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.croczilla.com/svg/samples/svgtetris/svgtetris.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Tetris</a>, <a href=\"https://www.codedread.com/yastframe.php\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Yet Another SVG Tetris</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://www.treebuilder.de/svg/connect4.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Connect 4</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://files.myopera.com/orinoco/svg/USStates.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Find the State</a> game</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.carto.net/papers/svg/us_population/index.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">US popuplation map</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://www.destatis.de/jetspeed/portal/cms/Sites/destatis/Internet/EN/Content/Statistics/Bevoelkerung/VorausberechnungBevoelkerung/InteraktiveDarstellung/Content75/Bevoelkerungspyramide1W1,templateId=renderSVG.psml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Germany\npopulation chart</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.treebuilder.de/default.asp?file=441875.xml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">3D box</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://www.treebuilder.de/default.asp?file=206524.xml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">3D boxes</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.amaltas.org/svgapp\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG+DOM based drawing tool</a></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"繪圖、圖表、遊戲 & 3D 實驗"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"關聯主題","title":"關聯主題","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/XML\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">XML</a>, <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"為何使用 SVG？","id":"為何使用_svg？"},{"text":"Mozilla 裡的 SVG","id":"mozilla_裡的_svg"},{"text":"工具","id":"工具"},{"text":"動畫和互動","id":"動畫和互動"},{"text":"繪圖、圖表、遊戲 &amp; 3D 實驗","id":"繪圖、圖表、遊戲_3d_實驗"},{"text":"關聯主題","id":"關聯主題"}],"summary":"由此開始\n  本教程將輔助你開始使用 SVG。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"SVG (Scalable Vector Graphics)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SVG: スケーラブルベクターグラフィック","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"SVG: Gráficos Vetoriais Escaláveis","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"SVG：可缩放矢量图形","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/svg","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/svg/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"}],"pageTitle":"SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}